{"uuid":"recommended208353","createDate":1760410023414,"customConfigJson":"{\"gameId\":\"208353\",\"readError\":\"false\",\"syncTime\":\"2024-04-30 17:03:53\",\"ratingSummary\":\"推荐\",\"postTime\":\"2019-10-06\",\"gameName\":\"Train Simulator: ScotRail Class 380 EMU Add-On\",\"gameLink\":\"https://store.steampowered.com/app/208353\",\"recommendedLink\":\"https://steamcommunity.com/id/oneness629/recommended/208353/\",\"playTime\":\"0.0\",\"updateTime\":\"2019-10-06\",\"reviewPlayTime\":\"0.0\",\"communityLink\":\"https://steamcommunity.com/app/208353\"}","type":"steamReview","title":"评测 > Train Simulator: ScotRail Class 380 EMU Add-On","content":"<div id=\"ReviewText\">\n 模拟火车：ScotRail Class 380 电力动车组\n <br>\n DLC只包含了Class 380 EMU，不包含任务，如果需要任务要额外购买线路\n <br>\n 不过听说买了线路后会自动有Class 380~亏了~就我傻乎乎地只买了车~emm~\n <br><a class=\"bb_link\" href=\"https://store.steampowered.com/app/24065/Train_Simulator_Glasgow_Airport_Rail_Link_Route_AddOn/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"\" id=\"dynamiclink_0\">https://store.steampowered.com/app/24065/Train_Simulator_Glasgow_Airport_Rail_Link_Route_AddOn/</a>\n <br>\n <br>\n 这车头也有通道，而且还是倾斜的~导致车头视野不怎么样~感觉这类地铁车厢似的多联装动车组都是这样~\n <br>\n 驾驶室电门操作按钮支持撒沙、紧急制动、单音喇叭（这车其实是双音喇叭的，驾驶室标识就有，但是DLC没做好）\n <br>\n 雨刷、车灯、受电弓~连仪表灯光开关都没有~\n <br>\n 驾驶室顶部有标识额定最高时速100mph~不过大家都知道额定时速都是用来超的~反正我没线路，就让我看看它能跑多快吧~\n <br><a class=\"bb_link\" href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=1882999749\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"\" id=\"dynamiclink_1\">https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=1882999749</a>\n <br>\n 妥妥地130mph+~虽然超过130加速就慢的很~那种短途客运每站都停基本也到不了这个速度~\n <br>\n 而且还能看到喇叭电门的高音低音标识，游戏里没做双音喇叭~\n</div>\n<div id=\"ReviewEdit\" style=\"display: none\">\n <textarea id=\"ReviewEditTextArea\" class=\"review_edit_text_area\" maxlength=\"8000\" rows=\"2\" cols=\"80\">模拟火车：ScotRail Class 380 电力动车组\nDLC只包含了Class 380 EMU，不包含任务，如果需要任务要额外购买线路\n不过听说买了线路后会自动有Class 380~亏了~就我傻乎乎地只买了车~emm~\nhttps://store.steampowered.com/app/24065/Train_Simulator_Glasgow_Airport_Rail_Link_Route_AddOn/\n\n这车头也有通道，而且还是倾斜的~导致车头视野不怎么样~感觉这类地铁车厢似的多联装动车组都是这样~\n驾驶室电门操作按钮支持撒沙、紧急制动、单音喇叭（这车其实是双音喇叭的，驾驶室标识就有，但是DLC没做好）\n雨刷、车灯、受电弓~连仪表灯光开关都没有~\n驾驶室顶部有标识额定最高时速100mph~不过大家都知道额定时速都是用来超的~反正我没线路，就让我看看它能跑多快吧~\nhttps://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=1882999749\n妥妥地130mph+~虽然超过130加速就慢的很~那种短途客运每站都停基本也到不了这个速度~\n而且还能看到喇叭电门的高音低音标识，游戏里没做双音喇叭~</textarea>\n <div class=\"review_edit_received_compensation\">\n  <input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"ReceivedCompensationCheckbox\" value=\"1\"> <label for=\"ReceivedCompensationCheckbox\">如果您是免费获取的此产品，请勾选此框 <a data-tooltip-text=\"如果您是免费获取的此产品，请勾选此框。您的评测旁会显示“免费获取的产品”。如果您评测此游戏还收到了其他报酬，必须在您的评测文本中披露。\">(?)</a></label>\n </div>\n <div style=\"float: left\">\n  您推荐这款游戏吗？ <span class=\"btnv6_blue_hoverfade btn_small_thin ico_hover active\" onclick=\"SetOwnerRatingPositive();\" id=\"OwnerVoteUpBtn\"> <span><i class=\"ico16 thumb_up\"></i> 是</span> </span> <span class=\"btnv6_blue_hoverfade btn_small_thin ico_hover \" onclick=\"SetOwnerRatingNegative();\" id=\"OwnerVoteDownBtn\"> <span><i class=\"ico16 thumb_down\"></i>否</span> </span>\n </div>\n <div style=\"float: right\">\n  <span class=\"btn_small_thin btn_grey_white_innerfade\" onclick=\"CancelEdits();\" id=\"CancelEditsBtn\"> <span>取消</span> </span> <span class=\"btn_small_thin btn_blue_white_innerfade\" onclick=\"SaveReview();\" id=\"SaveReviewBtn\"> <span>保存修改</span> </span>\n </div>\n <div style=\"clear: both\"></div>\n</div>","bgArchivesType":{"uuid":"d612b8f8-70ee-4b73-9f32-04475fbe954e","code":"Steam游戏评测","name":"Steam游戏评测","parentUuid":"a4fb2b94-3d2b-414d-8745-49677c3c7d22"}}